---
title: Sweet 'N' Savory Apricot Pork Chops over Ginger Rice with Marinated Bok Choy Salad
description: Think this is just another pork chop dinner? Think again—the lean meat travels into new territory with an Asian-inspired mix of sweet and savory. That’s thanks to the accompanying glaze, which blends together apricot jam, honey, and soy sauce. The sides also ride the East-meets-West flavor wave, featuring ginger-infused rice and crisp baby bok choy with optional slivers of fiery chili.
